INSERT INTO `blogs` VALUES (9,'HoaiThu','Haidilau.png','<h2>Haidilao Bitexco District 1 - Explore Space &amp; Services</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Cozy and Comfortable Space</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Haidilao Bitexco has a spacious, airy space, creating a cozy and relaxing feeling for diners. The lighting in the restaurant is designed to be moderate, not too bright or too dark, helping to create a pleasant dining space. The restaurant has many large tables, suitable for large groups, and also has a VIP room with karaoke services, speakers and modern entertainment equipment, ensuring you and your family or friends have the most relaxing and fun moments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungvt/blog_2024/haidilao_bitexco_blog/haidilao%20bitexco%201.png\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Excellent Service</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The highlight that makes many diners return to Haidilao Bitexco is the excellent service. The staff here are well-trained, always enthusiastic and friendly. From the moment you step in, you will be warmly welcomed and attentively supported. The restaurant also has special services such as nail salons, crane folding, and a snack bar with fruits and ice cream, making you feel taken care of from start to finish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One notable point is that the restaurant organizes birthday parties for customers very lovely and thoughtful. Besides, every time you leave, the restaurant also has beautiful gifts for you, creating more joy and satisfaction.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Menu, Food Menu At Haidilao Bitexco District 1</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Diverse and Quality Menu</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Regarding food, Haidilao Bitexco is famous for its rich and attractive hot pot dishes. You should not miss Haidilao Hot Pot and Uyen Uong Hot Pot - two signature dishes of the restaurant. In addition, the menu is also very diverse with dishes such as Haidilao beef, hazelnut shrimp, and many kinds of fresh seafood.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungvt/blog_2024/haidilao_bitexco_blog/haidilao%20bitexco%203.png\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The restaurant&#39;s line is always full, ensuring that the food is always fresh and served quickly. In particular, the dipping sauce at Haidilao is a big plus. If you know how to mix it, you will have a delicious, perfect bowl of dipping sauce to go with hot pot dishes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungvt/blog_2024/haidilao_bitexco_blog/haidilao%20bitexco%207.png\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For those who love dessert, Haidilao also does not disappoint with delicious ice creams such as melon and chocolate. The milk tea here is also delicious and is constantly refilled, ensuring you always have a delicious drink throughout the meal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungvt/blog_2024/haidilao_bitexco_blog/haidilao%20bitexco%204.png\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungvt/blog_2024/haidilao_bitexco_blog/haidilao%20bitexco%205.png\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungvt/blog_2024/haidilao_bitexco_blog/haidilao%20bitexco%206.png\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Amenities &amp; notes when eating at Haidilao Bitexco District 1</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3>Convenience and Friendliness</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Another big plus of Haidilao Bitexco is the convenient parking. The parking lot is located in the basement of Bitexco Tower, very easy to find. If you have a shopping bill of 300 thousand or more, you will be able to park your motorbike for free, helping you save money and enjoy your meal with peace of mind.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For families with children, Haidilao is a great choice. The restaurant space is spacious, airy and the staff is extremely friendly and enthusiastic, which will surely make the children love it. However, if you go with someone who needs to use a wheelchair, it may be a bit difficult because the restaurant is quite crowded and busy. But don&#39;t worry, the staff here are always willing to support you at any time.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Tips When Going to Haidilao Bitexco</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Because Haidilao Bitexco is always crowded, you should prioritize booking a table in advance to avoid having to wait long. You can contact the hotline for advice and reservations&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:02822539155\"><strong>CLICK HERE</strong></a>&nbsp;. The prices here are quite affordable, ranging from 300,000 to 400,000 VND/person, very reasonable for a delicious meal in the center of District 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The restaurant is open from 09:00 to 22:00, suitable for both lunch and dinner. The specific address is Bitexco Commercial Center, 2 Hai Trieu Street, Ben Nghe, District 1, Ho Chi Minh City 700000.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you have never been to Haidilao Bitexco, take the time to visit and experience the excellent service and delicious dishes here. Surely you will have memorable moments and want to come back again.</p>\r\n','2024-08-06 22:53:46.236000','If you are looking for a place that not only has delicious food but also offers great service right in the heart of District 1, Ho Chi Minh City, Haidilao Bitexco restaurant is definitely the perfect choice. Located on the 2nd floor of Bitexco Shopping Mall, Haidilao Bitexco is not only famous for its delicious hot pot dishes but also for the enthusiasm, friendliness and professionalism of its staff.','HOT','Discover Haidilao Bitexco Restaurant - Culinary Paradise in the Center of District 1','ACTIVE','2024-08-06 22:53:46.236000'),(10,'Trung','14quananngonnhatq1.jpg','<p><strong>Criteria for PasGo Team to select restaurants to include in this Collection:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>These are delicious restaurants in Hanoi that have cooperated with PasGo, get free reservations and receive incentives.</li>\r\n	<li>Restaurants have price ranges from affordable to high-end (from 250,000 VND/person).</li>\r\n	<li>Prioritize delicious restaurants with Hanoi identity and famous brands.</li>\r\n	<li>PasGo Team tries to choose many&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/quan-an-ngon-ha-noi-682\" target=\"_blank\">delicious restaurants and eateries in Hanoi</a>&nbsp;in different districts and areas so that customers can easily move around and book a table.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>I. List of delicious Vietnamese restaurants in Hanoi</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Want to enjoy familiar flavors from all three regions of the country? Check out the list of delicious Vietnamese restaurants in Hanoi below.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>1. The World of Seafood - Famous seafood restaurant in Hanoi</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price from 400,000 - 600,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to fresh seafood with top quality, we cannot help but mention The World of Seafood - a famous restaurant chain established in 2013. Fresh mantis shrimp, delicious lobster, creamy oysters,... are a few of the more than 100 types of fresh seafood you can find at this delicious restaurant in Hanoi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Please continue to explore more about the menu, space and promotions of The World of Seafood restaurant&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/the-gioi-hai-san-ha-noi-1073\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungtv/anh-bo-suu-tap/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-o-hn/top-nha-hang-ngon-hn.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>2. Song Duong Goat Meat - Famous delicious goat meat dish in Hanoi</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 280,000 - 300,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>When it comes to goat specialties in Hanoi, perhaps no place can surpass the De Re Song Duong chain. The menu has up to 39 delicious dishes made from goat such as grilled goat, goat with rice husks, goat sausage, raw goat with lemon... This place has become a favorite dining spot and delicious restaurant in Hanoi for many diners.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Book a table at De Re Song Duong restaurant&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/de-re-song-duong-1071\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;to receive unexpected offers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/thanhmai/anh-sua/de-re-song-duong-1.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&gt;&gt; See more:&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/lau-and-nuong-91\" target=\"_blank\">Discover ENDLESSLY delicious hot pot and grill restaurants in Hanoi | BOOK A TABLE TO GET DISCOUNTS</a></strong></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ho-chi-minh/nha-hang/lau-and-nuong-91\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Unlimited HOT POT GRILL restaurants for friends, colleagues, and relatives to enjoy in HCM</strong></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. Bien Dong Seafood Restaurant - The taste of the ocean in the middle of Hanoi city</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 250,000 - 400,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Coming to Bien Dong Seafood is coming to a &quot;miniature ocean&quot; with countless fresh seafood from popular to high-end, imported directly from Phu Quoc. The dishes here are not only fresh and delicious but also very affordable, suitable for family meals, company parties...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Book a table at Bien Dong Seafood&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/hai-san-bien-dong-233\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;to receive promotions from this delicious Hanoi restaurant!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 20 famous and most favorite delicious restaurants in Hanoi - 4\" src=\"https://pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungtv/anh-bo-suu-tap/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-o-hn/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-duoc-yeu-thich-nhat-o-ha-noi-4.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>4. Phuong Nam - Delicious Hanoi restaurant with full Southern flavor&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 150,000 - 200,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Phuong Nam is a chain of restaurants specializing in Southern dishes. Coming to the restaurant, you will enjoy Southern specialties in a spacious, cool space. Famous delicacies that make up the Phuong Nam brand: Crispy rice with caramelized fish sauce, goby fish hotpot, Southern Vietnamese pancakes, fish sauce hotpot...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Discover Phuong Nam restaurant&#39;s promotions and book a table at this delicious Hanoi restaurant&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/nha-hang-phuong-nam-1080\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungtv/anh-bo-suu-tap/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-o-hn/top-quan-an-gia-dinh-ngon-hn-1.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>5. Countryside Market - Rich in the flavor of the distant countryside&nbsp;</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 150,000 - 500,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Cho Que Restaurant is famous for its Vietnamese culinary flavors. This is a restaurant with a beautiful view and a space that preserves the simple Vietnamese countryside culture. Cho Que brings all the characteristics of each region wrapped up in each dish: Crispy fried chicken with sticky rice, fresh spring rolls with shrimp and meat, Tien Yen banana flower chicken salad...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; See details of promotions and book a table at Hanoi&#39;s delicious restaurant Cho Que&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/chuoi-cho-que-1745\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 20 famous and most favorite delicious restaurants in Hanoi - 2\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/vuvu/blog/top20nhahangngonhanoi/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-nhat-o-ha-noi-6.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&gt;&gt; See more:&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/chuyen-muc/nha-hang-dat-tiec-gia-dinh-o-ha-noi-vl8amm\" target=\"_blank\">Strengthen family ties with a meal at a cozy family restaurant in Hanoi</a></strong></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ho-chi-minh/nha-hang/quan-an-gia-dinh-hcm-502\" target=\"_blank\">Don&#39;t miss these 20 QUIET, COZY family restaurants and eateries in HCM | BOOK A TABLE NOW</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>6. Hue Features - Rich flavors of the Ancient Capital&#39;s cuisine</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 50,000 - 150,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Coming to Net Hue, you have the opportunity to enjoy and discover the unique quintessence of traditional Hue cuisine. Such as banh ram it, bun bo Hue, nem lui, oxtail stewed with five spices... The space of the Ancient Capital is represented, a blend of tradition and modernity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Discover Net Hue - A chain of delicious restaurants in Hanoi&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/net-hue-2059\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 20 famous and most favorite delicious restaurants in Hanoi - 14\" src=\"https://pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungtv/anh-bo-suu-tap/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-o-hn/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-duoc-yeu-thich-nhat-o-ha-noi-14.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>7. Cha Ca Hang Son - Delicious restaurant in Hanoi</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 200,000 - 300,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>We invite you to the Cha Ca Hang Son chain to fully experience the culinary quintessence of Cha Ca - a famous delicacy of the Imperial City. This is also one of the restaurants with beautiful views in Hanoi, bringing a gentle and cozy old space.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; See attractive promotions from Hanoi&#39;s delicious restaurant - Cha Ca Hang Son&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/cha-ca-hang-son-1604\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>II. Good restaurants in Hanoi serving Asian and European dishes</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you passionate about exploring world cuisine? Are you fascinated by the flavors of Japan, Korea, Thailand... or the delicately presented dishes of distant Italy... Then you should immediately refer to the list of delicious restaurants in Hanoi serving Asian and European dishes below!</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>1. Hatoyama &ndash; Japanese Taste Class</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 600,000 - 1,000,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The Hatoyama restaurant chain is attractive with a menu full of special dishes of Japanese cuisine. From sashimi and sushi dishes made from fresh seafood imported from Japan to premium, expensive beef such as Kobe beef, Wagyu beef,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; See details of space and menu of delicious restaurant Hatoyama Hanoi&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/hatoyama-1269\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 10 most famous, high-class restaurants in Hanoi 5\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/nguyendoan/anh-bo-suu-tap/10-nh-cao-cap-noi-tieng-o-hn/Top-10-nha-hang-cao-cap-noi-tieng-nhat-o-ha-noi-5a.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>2. King BBQ &ndash; Famous Korean BBQ King</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 250,000 - 400,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>King BBQ is a famous brand chain present across the country from North to South specializing in&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/ha-noi/nha-hang/han-quoc-16\" target=\"_blank\">Korean-style</a>&nbsp;grilled meat and hot pot . The menu of 200 dishes is served both buffet and a la carte, bringing exciting culinary experiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Book a table at King BBQ - Hanoi&#39;s delicious restaurant chain&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/chuoi-nha-hang/chuoi-king-bbq-ha-noi---nuong-lau-chuan-vi-xu-kim-chi-612\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;to receive incentives.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 20 famous and most favorite delicious restaurants in Hanoi - 5\" src=\"https://pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungtv/anh-bo-suu-tap/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-o-hn/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-duoc-yeu-thich-nhat-o-ha-noi-5.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&gt;&gt; See more:</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/chuyen-muc/nha-hang-dat-tiec-cong-ty-cho-moi-doan-lon-nho-tai-ha-noi-bu78gj\" target=\"_blank\">Top 10 BEST COMPANY PARTY Restaurants for all groups, big or small | GET DISCOUNTS</a></strong></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/chuyen-muc/nha-hang-dat-tiec-cong-ty-tai-ho-chi-minh-bgfbkq\" target=\"_blank\">Party hard at 50+ great restaurants for company parties in HCM | BOOK A TABLE NOW</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>3. Hotpot Story - Delicious Asian hotpot restaurant in Hanoi</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 250,000 - 400,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The story of 8 quintessential Asian hotpot flavors selected by Hotpot Story through the journey of discovery of culinary experts at Hotpot Story. The sour and spicy taste of Thai Toyum hotpot, spicy Sichuan hotpot, Japanese Miso hotpot, Korean Bulgogi hotpot...&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Please see more about the space and menu of Hotpot Story restaurant&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/chuoi-nha-hang/chuoi-nha-hang-hotpot-story-ha-noi---tinh-hoa-lau-chau-a-871\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;. Don&#39;t forget to book a table in advance through PasGo to receive incentives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Khao Lao Restaurant Chain\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/thanhmai/anh-sua/ha-hang-khao-lao-duy-tan-4.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>4. Al Fresco&#39;s Restaurant &ndash; Authentic Italian Pizza Flavor</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 95,000 - 395,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>The highlight at Al Fresco&#39;s - a chain of delicious restaurants in Hanoi that is loved by many young people, office workers, and families is the Italian pizzas with new variations in flavor and shape. From square, round to shrimp, beef,... all are prepared by the talented hands of experienced chefs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; Book a table at Al Fresco&#39;s restaurant with special offers&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/chuoi-nha-hang/chuoi-al-frescos-ha-noi---thuong-hieu-am-thuc-au---a-co-mat-tu-1996-793\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 20 famous and most favorite delicious restaurants in Hanoi - 10\" src=\"https://pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/dungtv/anh-bo-suu-tap/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-o-hn/top-20-nha-hang-ngon-noi-tieng-duoc-yeu-thich-nhat-o-ha-noi-10.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>5. Pepperonis - The story of the pioneer brand that brought Pizza to Vietnam</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Average price 130,000 - 150,000 VND/person</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Are you looking for a peaceful, quiet space to chat with friends and