00 VND/person</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 10 delicious and cheap BBQ buffet restaurants in Saigon photo 3\" src=\"https://pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/2amthuc/nhahang/top10buffetngonrehn/top-10-nha-hang-buffet-nuong-BBQ-ngon-re-o-Sai-Gon-3.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The beef is sliced ​​thick enough to create the moisture of the beef.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt; See more restaurant details&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/nha-hang/nha-hang-buffet-pachi-pachi-52-mac-dinh-chi-quan-1-712\" target=\"_blank\">here</a>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>3. Chen Buffet - 46 Thoai Ngoc Hau, Hoa Thanh ward, Tan Phu district</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>As a delicious and cheap barbecue buffet restaurant in Ho Chi Minh City, Chen Buffet is known for its rich and diverse 30-dish hot pot and barbecue buffet. Coming here, you will enjoy a variety of delicious dishes such as: grilled green crab, grilled oysters, beef rolls with mushrooms, grilled ribs, mushroom hot pot,... at extremely cheap prices!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Price range: from only 99,000 VND/person</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Top 10 delicious and cheap BBQ buffet restaurants in Saigon photo 5\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/2amthuc/nhahang/top10buffetngonrehn/top-10-nha-hang-buffet-nuong-tphcm-5.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fresh ingredients are well seasoned</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>4. Hell Bull BBQ &amp; Beer - 41 Xuan Thuy, Thao Dien ward, district 2&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Coming to Hell Bull BBQ &amp; Beer, you will enjoy an extremely rich and quality menu with a variety of dishes, not only BBQ from pork, beef, chicken to fresh seafood but also delicious and attractive Thai hot pot at cheap prices. This place is suitable for group meetings, parties or family gatherings...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Price range: 100,000 - 150,000 VND/person</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/napham/top%20nha%20hang%20bbq%20ngo