ceive incentives! Wish you have fun and meaningful moments with friends and relatives!</p>\r\n','2024-08-06 22:59:47.419000','Below are 10 attractive barbecue buffet restaurants in Ho Chi Minh City with delicious Korean and Japanese grilled dishes, clean and guaranteed ingredients and affordable prices. Check it out now!','HOT','Top 10 delicious and cheap BBQ buffet restaurants, price around 200k/person in Ho Chi Minh City','ACTIVE','2024-08-06 22:59:47.419000'),(12,'Hoang Lan','topquanbuffetlaunuong.jpg','<h2>1. Van Don Seafood Vo Thi Sau - Delicious seafood hotpot</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Address: No. 91 Vo Thi Sau - Thanh Nhan Ward - Hai Ba Trung District - Hanoi</li>\r\n	<li>Opening hours: 10:30 - 13:30 and 17:00 - 21:30</li>\r\n	<li>Price: From 200,000 VND - 300,000 VND</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Delicious seafood hotpot - Fresh seafood&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>If you are looking for a delicious Vo Thi Sau hot pot buffet address, you should immediately refer to the delicious Van Don seafood hot pot Vo Thi Sau. The restaurant&#39;s seafood is fresh and hand-caught, processed right at the table for diners to enjoy. The restaurant&#39;s famous delicious dishes include grilled, steamed, or baked bamboo lobster with cheese; King crab fried with salt, steamed, baked with cheese, fried with garlic; Steamed and fried Alaska lobster; Delicious seafood hot pot is also very attractive...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau hot pot and grill buffet Van Don Seafood\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-hai-san-van-don.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /><br />\r\n<em>Delicious Van Don seafood hotpot, fresh and delicious hotpot broth (Photo: PasGo Team)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The restaurant space is modern, spacious and airy with only 1 floor but can accommodate up to more than 550 diners. If you want a private space, you can book a private room. The restaurant also has outdoor tables to serve the needs of customers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau hot pot and grill buffet Van Don Seafood\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-hai-san-van-don-1.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Van Don seafood space is spacious and airy (Photo: PasGo Team)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Book Van Don Vo Thi Sau seafood restaurant via PasGo with many incentives&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Van Don Vo Thi Sau Seafood is a delicious restaurant that is often full and crowded, so customers should prioritize booking a table in advance and holding a seat to avoid running out of tables and not having to wait. To book a table and hold a seat most conveniently, you can refer to booking a table through PasGo with many incentives on costs, helping customers choose the most satisfactory seating position.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Luckily, Van Don Vo Thi Sau seafood restaurant is now available on the delicious restaurant booking platform PasGo. Refer to more information and book Van Don seafood restaurant on PasGo&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/nha-hang/hai-san-van-don-vo-thi-sau-3949\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;to receive immediate incentives.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>2. Khang Buffet Vo Thi Sau - Delicious grilled food for drinkers</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Opening hours: 18:00 - 23:00</li>\r\n	<li>Price: From 199,000 VND</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Khang Nuong Vo Thi Sau is a hot pot and grill restaurant serving both hot pot and grill at very reasonable prices starting from only 199,000 VND. The restaurant is always crowded with delicious hot pot and grill dishes at affordable prices, well-marinated grilled meat, and fresh hot pot ingredients.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Khang Buffet hot pot and grill buffet\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-khang-buffet.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Khang Buffet is a favorite Vo Thi Sau barbecue restaurant (Photo:st)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khang Buffet&#39;s hot pot and grill dipping sauce is a bit sweet in the Southern style, so it&#39;s not really suitable for some Northerners, which is considered a small minus point. The outdoor space is spacious and airy with a variety of drinks for diners to enjoy hot pot and grill while drinking. Unfortunately, Khang Buffet is not currently available on the online table booking platform - PasGo restaurant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PasGo update now Khang Buffet has moved to a new location!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>3. Hung Beo Vo Thi Sau Grilled Grill - Grilled buffet at &quot;student&quot; price</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Opening hours: 18:00 - 23:30</li>\r\n	<li>Price: Grill buffet 159,000 VND; Hot pot buffet 159,000 VND; Hot pot - grill combo 199,000 VND</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Grilled pork Hung Beo is considered a grilled buffet address Vo Thi Sau with super fresh and delicious food quality, especially enthusiastic staff and very reasonable prices, so it is loved by many diners. Hot pot and grilled buffet Vo Thi Sau, Hai Ba Trung district, Hanoi - Hung Beo is a sidewalk hot pot and grilled food address but the food quality is super delicious and the price is also very reasonable.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Hot pot and grill buffet Vo Thi Sau Hung Beo\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-hung-beo.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Hung Beo Vo Thi Sau grilled skewers are fresh and delicious (Photo:st)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The buffet menu of this Vo Thi Sau hot pot and grill restaurant is extremely diverse with dishes: grilled onion belly, grilled pork strips, grilled chicken wings, spicy cartilage ribs, special sausage, boneless chicken feet, butter bread,... The restaurant&#39;s hot pot buffet has American beef belly, beef tenderloin, beef tongue, beef balls, chicken thighs, fish cakes, intestines, cartilage,... The restaurant&#39;s drinks include beer, coca, red beef, simple iced tea for diners to choose to order when eating buffet. Unfortunately, Hung Beo Grilled Lui is not available on the online table booking platform - PasGo restaurant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&gt;&gt;&gt;See more:&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/blog/top-10-quan-an-ngon-nhat-khu-vuc-hai-ba-trung-542\" target=\"_blank\">Top best restaurants in Hai Ba Trung area</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>4. Grilled skewers of Map Coi Vo Thi Sau only 135,000 VND</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Opening hours: 18:30 - 23:00</li>\r\n	<li>Price range: from 50,000 VND - 135,000 VND</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Grilled ...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Hot pot buffet Vo Thi Sau grilled skewers Map Coi\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-map-coi.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Hot pot and grill buffet Vo Thi Sau Map Coi Delicious grilled food restaurant, comfortable space (Photo:st)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Map Coi Quan is considered a &quot;sidewalk restaurant&quot; with a student-priced grilled buffet, seafood is always fresh and delicious with octopus or squid eggs, beef, pork are all delicious and attractive. The restaurant also uses smokeless charcoal so it is extremely convenient and clean. The restaurant menu is diverse with delicious quality grilled dishes, diners can enjoy delicious grilled dishes such as: Sweet and sour grilled ribs, grilled octopus with pepper sauce, grilled offal with satay sauce, .. Unfortunately, Map Coi Quan is not currently available on the online table booking platform - PasGo restaurant</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>5. Korean hot pot and grill buffet Tugi House Vo Thi Sau</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Opening hours: 10:00 - 16:00 and 17:00 - 23:00</li>\r\n	<li>Price range: Grilled or hotpot buffet from 159,000 VND; Grilled and hotpot buffet from 199,000 VND</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Vo Thi Sau Hot Pot Buffet, Hai Ba Trung District, Hanoi - Tugi House is highly rated for the quality of its food. Vo Thi Sau Hot Pot Buffet is delicious and you definitely shouldn&#39;t miss this place. The beef dipped in the hot pot is fresh, the hot pot broth is clear and foam-free. Other toppings for dipping in the hot pot are also very attractive, including shrimp heads and attractive squid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Tugi House hot pot and grill buffet\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-tugi-house-1.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /><br />\r\n<em>Tugi House hot pot buffet with fresh beef, clear hot pot broth (Photo: st)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most popular grilled buffet at Vo Thi Sau at Tugi House is beef, marinated meat with rich flavor. The restaurant has tofu pudding for dessert for diners. The space is super beautiful, has air conditioning and a smoke extraction system to avoid too much smell when diners enjoy the hot pot and grilled buffet. Unfortunately, Tugi House is not currently available on the online table booking platform - PasGo restaurant</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Tugi House hot pot and grill buffet\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-tugi-house.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /><br />\r\n<em>Tugi House&#39;s homemade dipping sauce is diverse (Photo:st)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>6. Delicious Buffalo - Delicious buffalo hotpot restaurant in the Northwest</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Address: No. 91 Vo Thi Sau - Thanh Nhan Ward - Hai Ba Trung District - Hanoi</li>\r\n	<li>Opening hours: 10:30 - 23:00</li>\r\n	<li>Price: From 150,000 VND - 250,000 VND&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Delicious restaurant specializing in buffalo meat dishes</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to the Vo Thi Sau hot pot buffet, if you want to enjoy delicious hot pot, don&#39;t miss Trau Ngon Qua. Trau Ngon Qua has been operating for more than 3 years and has received a lot of love from Hanoi diners. All dishes are made from fresh, delicious buffalo meat, standard Northwest. The buffalo meat is very soft and not tough at all, retaining the characteristic sweetness of the meat.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The most famous delicious dishes at Trau Ngon Qua Vo Thi Sau that are loved by diners are Tay Bac Buffalo Hotpot, buffalo hotpot with fermented rice and buffalo rolls, fried buffalo with garlic, fried buffalo meat with green pepper, grilled buffalo on stone,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Hot Pot and Grill Buffet, So Delicious Buffalo\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-trau-ngon-qua-1.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /><br />\r\n<em>Super delicious Buffalo Hotpot (Photo:st)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The space of Trau Ngon Qua Vo Thi Sau is super spacious, over 1000m2 and right next to Thanh Nhan lake, airy and cool, so it is very suitable for gathering with friends and relatives.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Hot Pot and Grill Buffet, So Delicious Buffalo\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-trau-ngon-qua.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>The space of Trau Ngon Qua is super spacious and right next to Thanh Nhan Lake, super spacious and airy (Photo: st)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Book Trau Ngon Qua restaurant via PasGo with many incentives&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Trau Ngon Qua is a place to eat buffalo hotpot, buffalo dishes are extremely attractive and loved by many diners. However, if you do not book in advance at the restaurant, the table will be full very quickly and there will be no attractive promotions. PasGo is a platform that supports online table reservations for diners when coming to eat at Trau Ngon Qua with many promotions, helping you choose a satisfactory seat, book a seat in advance to avoid running out of tables during peak hours.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Don&#39;t forget to book a table and reserve a seat online at Trau Ngon Qua restaurant on PasGo&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://pasgo.vn/nha-hang/nha-hang-trau-ngon-qua---vo-thi-sau-4599\" target=\"_blank\">HERE</a></strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;to get a nice seat and many attractive price incentives.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>7. Gia Trang Quan - Traditional delicious hotpot, the quintessence of country cuisine</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Address: Lane 42 Vo Thi Sau - Hai Ba Trung District - Hanoi</li>\r\n	<li>Opening hours: 11:00 - 22:00</li>\r\n	<li>Price: From 150,000 VND - 250,000 VND</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3>Traditional food menu with unique names</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Vo Thi Sau Hot Pot is delicious, you should definitely visit Gia Trang Quan once with a super attractive menu with hot pot dishes with unique names: Long-legged frog hot pot, speeding snail hot pot, straight-walking crab hot pot, graceful eel hot pot, dying chicken hot pot, kimchi cheese hot pot. In addition, the restaurant has super delicious and attractive catfish sets, sturgeon sets, eel, Thi No chicken porridge hot pot.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Gia Trang Quan hot pot and grill buffet\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-gia-trang-quan.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Gia Trang Quan hot pot set with traditional flavor (Photo: PasGo Team)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Diners can also enjoy special dishes such as Vu Dai village sticky rice, Gia Trang grilled chicken, Hoang Pho sticky rice,... Gia Trang Quan space is especially large and has an ancient look with a design like a miniature Vu Dai village.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Gia Trang Quan hot pot and grill buffet\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-gia-trang-quan-2.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Vo Thi Sau hot pot and grill is delicious, high-class with buffalo meat dishes that cannot be missed at Gia Trang Quan (Photo: PasGo Team)</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Vo Thi Sau Gia Trang Quan hot pot and grill buffet\" src=\"https://cdn.pastaxi-manager.onepas.vn/content/uploads/articles/lanmkt/quananoquanhbt/buffetlaunuongvothisau/buffet-lau-nuong-vo-thi-sau-gia-trang-quan-3.jpg\" style=\"height:auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>Gia Trang Quan&#39;s space is super spacious, decorated with bold rustic colors (Photo: PasGo Team)</em></p>\r\n','2024-08-06 23:01:30.859000','Cheap hot pot and grill buffet Vo Thi Sau Hanoi near Tuoi Tre Park for drinkers, company parties, and festivals is extremely reasonable. Join PasGo to check out the best hot pot and grill buffet restaurants on Vo Thi Sau Street, Hanoi','NOT','Top best hot pot and grill buffet restaurants on Vo Thi Sau - NEAR Tuoi Tre park','ACTIVE','2024-08-06 23:01:30.859000');
